       <div class="footer-widget">
        <div id="text-3" class="f_widget widget_text">
         <h4 class="widgettitle">Message</h4> 
         <div class="textwidget">
          <img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-156" alt="IMG_5265" src="http://ndub.edu.bd/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/IMG_5277-150x150.jpg" width="150" height="150">Notre Dame University Bangladesh received the official approbation of the Government of Bangladesh on 29th April 2013. This news of great joy was especially welcomed by the members of the Congregation of Holy Cross all over the world, the Catholic Church in Bangladesh and the Alumni of Notre Dame College. We are deeply grateful to the Hon'ble Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina and His Excellency, Dr. A K Azad Chowdhury (State Minister &amp; Chairman of the University Grants Commission), for this great favour. On behalf of the University and the Congregation of Holy Cross and on my own behalf I convey our deep gratitude to them. 
