         <h4 class="widgettitle">Message</h4> 
         <div class="textwidget">
          As an alumna of Notre Dame College, I consider it a great honour and a privilege to be a member of the Board of Trustees of Notre Dame University Bangladesh, a long cherished dream. I feel happy to be involved in the planning and implementation of the project at the initial stage. I sincerely hope that the NDUB will make a Big Life-changing Impact on the lives of students who enroll themselves here for Excellence and Bright Future through Quality Education. I also wish and hope that more and more alumni, well-wishers, benefactors, friends and students will come forward to support NDUB, especially in the initial stage of its journey. 
